CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780138973
OL,3,CThousands without water for seventh
OL,4,Cday after reservoirs 'reach critical
OL,5,Clevel'
OL,7,FThousands of people in Whitstable are
OL,8,Fstill without water supply during the
OL,9,Fhot spell of weather as storage
OL,10,Freservoirs for the area "reached a
OL,11,Fcritical level", South East Water said.
OL,13,FQueues of people lined up at a bottled
OL,14,Fwater collection point at a
OL,15,FSainsbury's, as the water company said
OL,16,F8,000 customers were without supply.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
