OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780138973
OL,3,CThousands without water for seventh
OL,4,Cday after reservoirs 'reach critical
OL,5,Clevel'
OL,7,F"I'm not going to give my customers
OL,8,Fsubstandard food," he said.
OL,10,FEarlier this month South East Water's
OL,11,Fchief executive David Hinton announced
OL,12,Fhis plans to step down just a week
OL,13,Fafter the group's chairman Chris Train
OL,14,Fquit following a scathing report by
OL,15,FMPs, who said they had "no confidence"
OL,16,Fin the company's leadership.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@RO]wD@XOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780138973
OL,3,CThousands without water for seventh
OL,4,Cday after reservoirs 'reach critical
OL,5,Clevel'
OL,7,FThe scrutiny came after thousands of
OL,8,Fcustomers were left unable to access
OL,9,Ftap water, shower or flush their
OL,10,Ftoilets during the outages between
OL,11,FNovember and January.
OL,13,FDry Wells Action, a consumer action
OL,14,Fgroup based in Tunbridge Wells, said
OL,15,Fthe latest outages show South East
OL,16,FWater has "learned nothing from the
OL,17,Fcatastrophic Tunbridge Wells water
OL,18,Fcrisis".
OL,26,@xD@KOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780138973
OL,3,CThousands without water for seventh
OL,4,Cday after reservoirs 'reach critical
OL,5,Clevel'
OL,7,FGroup chairman Jonathan Hawker said:
OL,8,F"How can South East Water still be
OL,9,Fgetting the basics of crisis response
OL,10,Fso badly wrong?
OL,12,F"Customers were promised lessons would
OL,13,Fbe learned. These latest failures
OL,14,Fdemonstrate, once again, it's all talk
OL,15,Fand no action. The licence of this
OL,16,Fwater monopoly that cannot deliver
OL,17,Fshould surely now be revoked."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780138973
OL,3,CThousands without water for seventh
OL,4,Cday after reservoirs 'reach critical
OL,5,Clevel'
OL,7,FMeanwhile Kent County Council said it
OL,8,Fwill set up a new "strategic
OL,9,Fpartnership" to oversee water
OL,10,Fresilience in the county following the
OL,11,Flatest outages.
OL,13,FThe Kent Water Resilience Partnership
OL,14,Fwill be chaired by council leader
OL,15,FLinden Kemkaran and include water
OL,16,Fcompanies, local authorities,
OL,17,Fregulators and others to focus on
OL,18,Fplanning, performance and show
OL,19,Fpublicly how water issues are being
OL,20,Faddressed.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780138973
OL,3,CThousands without water for seventh
OL,4,Cday after reservoirs 'reach critical
OL,5,Clevel'
OL,7,FMs Kemkaran said: "People across Kent
OL,8,Fare fed up with being left without
OL,9,Fwater or having their supply
OL,10,Fdisrupted, sometimes for days at a
OL,11,Ftime, and not getting clear answers
OL,12,Fabout what's gone wrong or when it
OL,13,Fwill be fixed.
OL,15,F"That's simply not good enough."
OL,17,FThe council boss said while the
OL,18,Fauthority does not have direct power
OL,19,Fover water companies, "we do have a
OL,20,Fresponsibility to stand up for Kent".
OL,26,@oD@SOUwD@AOUwD@`O]{D@WOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
